{"tid":2264028,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"休班警藏毒罪成判入戒毒所　辯方求情指屢拘毒犯　水官：知法犯法無加刑已好客氣","createTime":"2020-10-30T10:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:22:40.000Z","uid":230530,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c0726f907ddb6fbc17a918bffe9f8a7388b6e30c","tid":2264028,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"確診武漢肺炎的休班男警，去年 2 月在新屯門中心遭同袍截查，涉搜出價值 660 元俗稱「K仔」的氯胺酮。被告陳天賜早前經審訊後，被裁定藏毒罪成。辯方求情時稱，被告27 年來為社會服務，亦多次拘捕毒犯。裁判官水佳麗今（30 日）在屯門裁判法院判刑時稱，不認同被告上周為販毒案作供可獲減刑，明言「係佢責任所在」。被告由 2008 年起吸毒，水佳麗認為他吸毒成癮，同時帶給家人難以承受的結果。她又稱：「警員知法犯法，無加刑已經好客氣」，終判被告入戒毒所。"},{"pid":"962becc25ff119e288b24d4c6d1b980b28d4e3bb","tid":2264028,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"水佳麗認為應先處理被告戒毒問題，指他保釋期間仍繼續吸毒，明顯有毒癮問題。辯方再次索取感化令報告，遭水官拒絕。她指被告作為警務人員，看到毒販不作拘捕，反而向他購買毒品，對他的選擇感到遺憾，「警員知法犯法，無加刑已經好客氣。」辯方向被告索取指示後，希望法庭判以監禁，因擔心在戒毒所再接觸吸毒人士，進入該圈子。"},{"pid":"a752abcb2f3985d3c92c4a0d1a3458965d486b3e","tid":2264028,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a